         <div xml:id="alalal-g98708"><!-- l4d15a2 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-g98708-Hd1e99">Articulus 2</head>
            <head xml:id="alalal-g98708-Hd1e101" type="question-title">An pro uno peccato potest consurgere 
duplex tribulatio ?</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e104">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="55"/>ARTICULUS II.
<lb ed="#Be" n="56"/>An pro uno peccato potest consurgere 
du<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="57"/>plex tribulatio ?
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e113">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="58"/>Deinde queritur de illo quod dicitur,
<lb ed="#Be" n="59"/>ibi, A, sub initio: <quote xml:id="alalal-g98708-Qd1e119"> Non consurget 
du<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="60"/>plex tribulaivo, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e125">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="61"/>Videtur contrarium
<lb ed="#Be" n="62"/>1. In Psalmo cv, 29, ubi dicitur:
<lb ed="#Be" n="63"/>Operiantur sicut diploide confusione sua.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="64"/>2. Item, Eccli: x1, 16: Hrror et tenebre
<lb ed="#Be" n="65"/>peccatoribus concreata sunt.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e142">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="66"/>3. Item, In Psalmo cxivui, 8: Ignis,
<lb ed="#Be" n="67"/>grando, nix, etc.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e149">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="68"/>Soxtutio. Dicendum, quod duplex 
tri<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="69"/>bulatio non consurget pro peccato quod
<lb ed="#Be" n="70"/>simpliciter est unum: sed quod est
<lb ed="#Be" n="71"/>unum subjecto, et plura deformitate : vel
<lb ed="#Be" n="72"/>pro pluribus peccalis bene consurget
<lb ed="#Be" n="73"/>duplex tribulatio ; sicut cum peccati 
ac<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="74"/>tus est unus, est tamen ibi libido, et 
con<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="75"/>temptus, et hujusmodi, quibus aliquid
<lb ed="#Be" n="76"/>respondet in poenis.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e171">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="77"/>Unde dicendum ad primum, quod hoc
<lb ed="#Be" n="78"/>non intelligitur ratione diversarum 
pe<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="79"/>narum debitarum uni pecc√©ato, sed 
ratio<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="80"/>neduarum partium ipsius peccantis, quae
<lb ed="#Be" n="81"/>sunt corpus et anima : et sicut peccavit
<lb ed="#Be" n="82"/>in corpore et anima, ita etiam punitur
<lb ed="#Be" n="83"/>in utroque.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e189">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="84"/>Ad aliud dicendum, quod hoc 
intel<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="85"/>ligitur ratione privationis habitus 
diri<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="86"/>geniis in ponis moribus. Error enim
<pb ed="#Be" n="473"/>
               <cb ed="#Be" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#Be" n="1"/>est in eligendo, et tenebree in 
providen<lb break="no" ed="#Be" n="2"/>do quid agendum sit.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-g98708-d1e207">
               <lb ed="#Be" n="3"/>Ad aliud dicendum, quod ille pone
<lb ed="#Be" n="4"/>non respondent uni peccato simpliciter,
<lb ed="#Be" n="5"/>sed pluribus, vel peccato quod unum est
<lb ed="#Be" n="6"/>subjecto, et multa deformitate.
</p>
